# Input
```html
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->
<div style="color: red;"></div>

<p style="font-size: 14px;">Hello</p>

<span style="display: none;">Hidden</span>

<input type="text" style="border: 1px solid black;" />

<a href="#" style="text-decoration: none;">Link</a>

```

